  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is a prospective, multicenter, randomized, single-blinded study to assess the
      safety and effectiveness of FIRM procedures followed by conventional ablation including PVI
      versus a standard PVI procedure for the treatment of persistent atrial fibrillation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
